Some jurisdictions, such as the European Union, China, Canada and United States, are in the process of <a1_0><b6_0>phasing out the use of incandescent light bulbs<b6_0/><a1_0/> while others, including Colombia, Mexico, Cuba, Argentina, Brazil and Australia, have <a0_0>prohibited them already<a0_0/>.
